(2182, 225, 'guest_bio', 'Alisha Ramos is a Product Design Director at <a href="http://www.voxmedia.com">Vox Media in D.C.</a>, where she works on building and scaling revenue platforms. She writes a weekly newsletter on mixed-race identity and other personal reflections call Mixed Feelings. She''ll never say no to a doughnut.'),
